Is It Here Yet?
===============

Copyright 2011 Matthew Lam
http://www.reservedbits.com/javawork/isithereyet

Overview
--------

Is It Here Yet? is a simple Android application that reads the
NextBus public XML feed and displays the arrival times for
transit vehicles for a chosen stop.

Is It Here Yet? is free software: you can redistribute it and/or
modify it under the terms of the GNU General Public License as
published by the Free Software Foundation, either version 3 of the
License, or (at your option) any later version.

Requirements
------------

Is It Here Yet? was developed for Android 3.0. It has only been
tested on an Android 3.0 emulator.

Warning
-------

NextBus periodically improves the XML feed format. This may cause
Is It Here Yet? to fail, and require fixing.

Disclaimer
----------

Is It Here Yet? merely uses NextBus' public data feed and is
otherwise not associated with NextBus. To learn more about NextBus
visit: http://www.nextbus.com/homepage/